          "description": "Find a level's runtime TileMap by the LDtk level identifier, or undefined when no level with that name exists. Searches across import('./ldtkLevelEntries').getLdtkLevelEntries's flattened level set rather than data.levels directly, so this works for both single-world and multi-world documents — data.levels alone is empty for the latter. The lookup is O(n) in the number of levels."
